briefdescription.para: Character type of error messages.

detaileddescription.para: The default character type is char. On Windows, user can define this macro as TCHAR for supporting both unicode/non-unicode settings.

briefdescription.para: Macro for converting string literial to RAPIDJSON_ERROR_CHARTYPE[].

detaileddescription.para: By default this conversion macro does nothing. On Windows, user can define this macro as _T(x) for supporting both unicode/non-unicode settings.
